    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This chicken got hands is an action arcade fighting game where you will be fighting against hordes of enemies to achieve a single goal of saving your eggs.   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into the &quot;feathery&quot; shoes of the boldest chicken ever in This Chicken Got Hands! In this action-packed, adrenaline-fueled  game, you take on the role of a blue and pink chicken on a mission to rescue your stolen eggs from the clutches of a sneaky farmer. But this isn’t just any rescue operation, prepare to destroy, smash, and wreak havoc to get your eggs back!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138140/extras/9f467c905e51608b22680239d6fae646.poster.avif?t=1738740439\" width=800 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138140/extras/9f467c905e51608b22680239d6fae646.webm?t=1738740439\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138140/extras/9f467c905e51608b22680239d6fae646.mp4?t=1738740439\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Be careful, some of his guys are really tough, you must be tactical enough in finding food to restore your health, and keeping your energy at a steady rate to use your special abilities.</p>",
